trans-unit.source: Represents the data of a property for a selected item and enables editing of this property with type-specific data.
trans-unit.target: 선택된 항목의 속성 데이터를 나타내며, 형식별 데이터를 사용하여 이 속성을 편집할 수 있도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class.
Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class.
The parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.

Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class that serves as a subproperty of the specified <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />의 하위 속성 역할을 하는 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: For host infrastructure derived classes.
The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> to apply.
Stores whether the target property value matches a specified <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" />.
trans-unit.target: 대상 속성 값이 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" />와 일치하는지 여부를 저장합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the category in which this property resides.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성이 있는 범주의 이름을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the category.
Enables the host infrastructure to create a new host-specific <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 호스트 인프라에서 호스트별 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 인스턴스를 새로 만들 수 있도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A new <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> object.
Gets the description of the encapsulated property.
A string that contains the description.
Gets the display name for the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
A string that contains the display name.

Declaration of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> event, which occurs when a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> is changed through a call to the <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> 메서드에 대한 호출을 통해 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" />가 변경될 때 발생하는 <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" /> 이벤트 선언입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether a set of standard values is available for this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />에 대해 표준 값 집합을 사용할 수 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if a set of standard values is available; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 표준 값 집합을 사용할 수 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> is custom-made.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />가 사용자 지정으로 작성되었는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property entry is custom-made; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성 항목이 사용자 지정으로 작성되었으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />이 읽기 전용인지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property entry is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성 항목이 읽기 전용이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> matches the filter.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" />이 필터와 일치하는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value to indicate that the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> matches the filter and fires the event handler method for the property change.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" />이 필터와 일치함을 나타내는 값을 설정하고 속성 변경에 대한 이벤트 처리기 메서드를 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the target object matches the filter; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 대상 개체가 필터와 일치하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `PropertyContainer` listens to changes made to this property.
trans-unit.target: `PropertyContainer`는 이 속성에 대한 변경 내용을 수신합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.String" /> display or type name of a filter to match against the target object.
trans-unit.target: 대상 개체와 비교할 필터의 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 표시 또는 형식 이름입니다.

trans-unit.source: Implementation of a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> method that determines whether the target display or type name matches the specified string containing the name of a filter.
trans-unit.target: 대상 표시 또는 형식 이름이 필터 이름을 포함하는 지정된 문자열과 일치하는지 확인하는 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> 메서드의 구현입니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the target display or type name matches the specified string; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 대상 표시 또는 형식 이름이 지정된 문자열과 일치하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> to apply.
Raises the <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.FilterApplied" /> event.
Raises the <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.PropertyChanged" /> event.
The EventArgs for this event.
Raises the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> PropertyChanged event.
The name of the property whose value has changed.

Raises the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> event when the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer" /> hears that the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> has changed.
Gets the parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> in classes derived from a host infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: 호스트 인프라에서 파생된 클래스에서 부모 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
This is used only for subproperties, so its value can be `null`.
trans-unit.target: 해당 값이 될 수 있도록 하위 속성에만 사용 되며이 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: Declaration of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> event, which occurs when a property value changes.
trans-unit.target: 속성 값이 변경되면 발생하는 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> 이벤트의 선언입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the property.
A string that contains the property name.
Gets the type of the property.
A type that contains the type of the property.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> for this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> object.

Gets the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> that is used for editing the value of this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" />의 값을 편집하는 데 사용되는 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> object that contains the current editor.
Gets a set of possible values supported by this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />에서 지원하는 가능한 값의 집합을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> of possible values.
